| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|--------|----------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/subscription/create-checkout` | JWT | Create Stripe checkout session |
| POST | `/subscription/cancel` | JWT | Cancel subscription |
| GET | `/subscription/status` | JWT | Get plan & usage info |
